sect1.sect2:
Introdução a LibreOffice
LibreOffice is a full-featured office suite. It is largely compatible with Microsoft Office and is descended from OpenOffice.org.
&lfs113_checked;
Informação do Pacote
Core Download:
Core Download MD5 sum: &libreoffice-core-md5sum;
Core Download size: &libreoffice-core-size;
Espaço em disco estimado exigido: &libreoffice-buildsize;
Tempo de construção estimado: &libreoffice-time;
Transferências Adicionais
Around 80 smallish tarballs and zip files will be downloaded during the build. The download time will vary with the local internet speed and server load. The download time is about 3 mn on a fiber connection, probably not much more than 10 mn on an ADSL connection. If you have not downloaded one or more of the following, they too will also be downloaded during the build.
Dictionaries:
Dictionaries MD5 sum: &libreoffice-dict-md5sum;
Dictionaries size: &libreoffice-dict-size;
Help Files:
Help Files MD5 sum: &libreoffice-help-md5sum;
Help Files size: &libreoffice-help-size;
Translations:
Translations MD5 sum: &libreoffice-translations-md5sum;
Translations size: &libreoffice-translations-size;
Dependências de LibreOffice
Exigida
